	$translation_38 = __("Based on Michelle Cummingsí best-selling book, this module (and the huge handout that comes with it), will give you fresh ideas for fast-moving icebreakers, group problem-solving games, and daily debriefing activities. All you need is an old deck of cards, a new group of young people, and your energy and imagination. Promote insight, friendship, understanding, and fun!", "EOT_LMS");
	$translation_39 = __("Because your brain first processes the positive in any statement, it can be confusing and ineffective to give campers a string of negative admonishments. A better way to achieve compliant behavior is to explain games, rules, and activities using positive statements. The examples in this original module show you how to turn \"Don't cross the line\" into \"Stay on your side\" with marvelous results.", "EOT_LMS");
