	$translation_52 = __("Building on the sage advice in Part I, this module references ancient Jewish teachings to explain how temperament affects behavior, how being proactive promotes success, how acceptance of differences is socially healthy and how personal renewalóespecially forgivenessóis good for the soul and the organization you serve. A playful and insightful module that will leave you inspiredÖwhatever your faith.", "EOT_LMS");
